---
title: Fried Turkey with Tomato Gravy and Roasted Broccoli
description: This is the kind of October meal that is sure to stick to your ribs. Pan fried turkey breast smothered in a rich creamy tomato gravy over fluffy mashed potatoes. Warm and hearty...the perfect fall combo!
